summary: An ordinance authorizing the dismissal of the suit providing for the condemnation, appropriation, taking and damaging of land and other property necessary for the laying off, widening, extending, altering and establishing of 9th Avenue West, 8th Avenue West, West Armour Street, West Ray Street and West Halladay Street, under Ordinance No. 22602, Cause No. 71543, insofar as the same affects lots 1 to 9, inclusive, in block 1; lots 1 to 11, inclusive, in block 2, and lots 1 to 10, inclusive, in block 3, in Sound View Addition to the City of Seattle.
